IMPLEMENTATION DECISIONS
------------------------
- **Module:** `crates/worker/src/task_execution.rs`, public via `lib.rs` as
  `pub mod task_execution`; `execute_pulled_task` is the entry used by pull loop.
- **Work dir:** `<REMOTE_HARNESS_WORK_DIR>/jobs/<job_id>/`; `remove_dir_all` then
  `create_dir_all` then fresh `clone_repository` every job (documented in worker
  README + plan complete notes). Default `REMOTE_HARNESS_WORK_DIR` =
  `{temp}/remote_harness_worker_jobs`.
- **Heartbeats:** `Arc<Mutex<Option<String>>>` shared with background interval;
  sends `heartbeat_idle` vs `heartbeat_busy(worker_id, job_id)` while executing.
- **Control plane client extensions:** `heartbeat_busy`, `post_task_logs`
  (202 ACCEPTED), `complete_task` (parses JSON `TaskCompleteResponse`),
  `complete_task_failed` wraps `complete_task` with failed body.
- **Git (`git_ops.rs`):**
  - `is_file_remote_url` + branches in `clone_repository`, `fetch_origin`,
    `push_refspec` for `file://` without token (dev/tests).
  - `working_tree_clean`, `head_oid_hex`, `current_branch_name`,
    `create_branch_from_head`.
- **branch_mode:**
  - `pr`: `create_branch_from_head` with `{branch_name_prefix}/job-<hex>` default
    prefix `rh/`, slug from first 8 hex chars of job UUID (fallback padding).
  - `main`: use current branch name if any; else `rh/job-<hex>` from detached HEAD.
- **Agent:** real path uses `build_invocation` + `run_invocation` with `TeeSink`
  (tracing + ordered lines for logs). Stub: `REMOTE_HARNESS_STUB_AGENT` in
  {1,true,yes} writes `.remote-harness-stub`, stdout from
  `REMOTE_HARNESS_STUB_AGENT_STDOUT` or default `stub agent ok\n`. Stub skips
  empty `agent_token` check; HTTPS still requires non-empty `git_token` unless
  `file://` remote.
- **Prompt composition:** `compose_prompt` merges `prompt_context`, chat follow-up
  fields (`session_prompt`, `history`/`history_assistant`, `message`), or
  `extract_prompt` for simple/loop shapes, plus optional `iteration` line.
- **Complete payload:**
  - `chat`: `assistant_reply` from stdout snippet (capped); `output` None.
  - `loop_until_sentinel`: `output` combined snippet, `sentinel_reached` from
    case-sensitive `.contains` on `params.sentinel`.
  - Other workflows: `output` Some(combined), no sentinel/assistant special case.
  - Agent non-zero: failed complete with `error_message` about exit status,
    optional output snippet.
  - After success: if working tree clean → skip commit/push, still success with
    current `commit_ref`/`branch`. Else `commit_all` then `push_refspec`; failures
    → failed complete with git error text (ARCHITECTURE §9a style).
  - `mr_title` only when `branch_mode == pr`, value `Harness: <branch>` — explicit
    suggestion only, not a claim that an MR exists.
- **Re-export:** `pub use api_types::PullTaskResponse` from worker `lib.rs` for
  integration tests / callers.

